\Leftrightarrow \|Ax\| = \|x\|
\|A\| \times \sqrt{<x,x>}
 A \quad \text{orthogonal} \qquad \Longleftrightarrow \qquad || Ax|| = ||x|| \quad \text{for all} \quad x \ . 
A
 ||Ax||^2 = (Ax)^t(Ax) = x^t(A^tA)x = x^tx = ||x||^2 \ , \quad \text{for all} \quad x \ . 
 x^ty =\frac{1}{2} \left( ||x+y||^2 - ||x||^2 - ||y||^2  \right) \ . 
\|x\|^2=x^tx
